直到1955年，巴寶莉品牌一直是独立公司，此年被ＧＵＳ公司（Great Universal Stores）收购。

自20世纪中叶，纺织业普及[[化学纤维|化学纤维]]，可制作更为轻便防水的服装。嘎巴甸的实用意义减小，转而成为奢侈品，博柏利的产品也从防风防寒的特殊服装转向时装市场。

20世纪70年代，巴寶莉品牌为英国足球流氓文化中的“休闲”（Casuals）[[亚文化|亚文化]]人士所热衷，以致到了90年代巴寶莉在英国主要和足球流氓团伙联系起来，到了20世纪末则成为“Chav”（教育程度较低、着装品味较差的社会底层年轻人）。
<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/chinese/trad/hi/newsid_4500000/newsid_4506200/4506228.stm |title=時尚觀察：Prav大戰Chav - BBC News |accessdate=2013-12-03 |archive-date=2013-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131207052436/http://news.bbc.co.uk/chinese/trad/hi/newsid_4500000/newsid_4506200/4506228.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |first=Julia |last=Day |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2004/nov/01/marketingandpr |title=Burberry doffs its cap to 'chavs' |work=Guardian |location=UK |date=1 November 2004 |accessdate=4 January 2011 |archive-date=2012-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121116042949/http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2004/nov/01/marketingandpr |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://money.guardian.co.uk/businessnews/story/0,1265,-1592049,00.html |title='This is perfect for Burberry' |publisher=Money.guardian.co.uk |date= |accessdate=4 January 2011 |archive-date=2013-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921061513/http://money.guardian.co.uk/businessnews/story/0,1265,-1592049,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

为了应对这一变化，巴寶莉进行了一系列的品牌拯救措施，例如在1998年将品牌名改回“Burberry”。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.vogue.com/voguepedia/Burberry |title='Burberry - Voguepedia' |publisher=Vogue |accessdate=7 June 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130616224351/http://www.vogue.com/voguepedia/Burberry |archivedate=2013年6月16日 |df= }}</ref>

===21世纪===
2001年，巴寶莉改聘设计师贝利（Christopher Bailey）為創意總監，同時改用PRORSUM作為時裝秀發表系列。<ref name="Times Sep 09">{{cite news |first=Colin |last=McDowell |title=Christopher Bailey: Burberry's golden boy |url=http://women.timesonline.co.uk/tol/life_and_style/women/fashion/article6817273.ece |work=The Times |date=6 September 2009 |accessdate=7 December 2009 |archive-date=2011-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110810080706/http://women.timesonline.co.uk/tol/life_and_style/women/fashion/article6817273.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |first=Dolly |last=Jones |title=All Hail Bailey |url=http://www.vogue.co.uk/news/daily/091111-burberry-creative-director-christop.aspx |work=Vogue |date=11 November 2009 |accessdate=7 December 2009 |archive-date=2009-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091114102153/http://www.vogue.co.uk/news/daily/091111-burberry-creative-director-christop.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>股东GUS在2005年抛售剩余股份，退出了Burberry。<ref>{{Cite web |first=Julia |last=Finch |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/business/2005/nov/18/3 |title=GUS shareholders to receive Burberry cheque |publisher=Guardian News and Media |date=18 November 2005 |accessdate=4 January 2011 |archive-date=2007-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071221011305/http://www.guardian.co.uk/business/2005/nov/18/3 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

Burberry集团于2002年在伦敦上市。同时，Burberry继续推进亚洲生意，2005年日本成衣销售额达到4.35亿欧元。<ref name="Luxury">{{cite book | title=Luxury Brand Management | publisher=John Wiley & Sons | author=Chevalier, Michel | year=2012 | location=Singapore | isbn=978-1-118-17176-9}}</ref>[[File:HK_TST_Sogo_shop_Burberry_night_visitors.JPG|thumb]]的博柏利门店]]

2006年，Angela Ahrendts上任Burberry執行長，改变了之前的通过商标授权达到大众市场的策略，<ref>[http://special.hsmglobal.com/us/wbfny2011/ahrendts-info.php Angela Ahrendts Biography] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150521044059/http://special.hsmglobal.com/us/wbfny2011/ahrendts-info.php |date=2015-05-21 }}</ref>并着手改变“Chav”形象，包括在公司的90%的产品上不再使用Vintage格纹，并将西班牙授权生意（占集团营业额的20%）回收。<ref name="Times Sep 09" /><ref name=WSJInt>{{Cite web |url=http://magazine.wsj.com/features/the-big-interview/earning-her-strips/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-12-03 |archive-date=2010-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100911195704/http://magazine.wsj.com/features/the-big-interview/earning-her-strips/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2006年开始，Burberry在美国、英国和欧盟陆续开始网上销售。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://uk.burberry.com/pws/ProductCategoryAttributeLink.ice?paId=SHOP-BY-DEPARTMENT&layout=departmenthome.layout&page=ShopOnline |title=Shop on line |publisher=Uk.burberry.com |date=5 December 2010 |accessdate=4 January 2011 |archive-date=2008-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080430193658/http://uk.burberry.com/pws/ProductCategoryAttributeLink.ice?paId=SHOP-BY-DEPARTMENT&layout=departmenthome.layout&page=ShopOnline |dead-url=no }}</ref>

近年，Burberry开始在时尚杂志上刊登广告，并聘用知名演员、模特出镜，例如2009到2010年的[[艾瑪·沃特森|艾瑪·沃特森]]。<ref>{{Cite web |first=Carly |last=Zinderman |url=http://www.ibtimes.com/contents/20090715/grown-emma-watson-models-burberry.htm |title=A Grown-up Emma Watson Models for Burberry |publisher=International Business Times |date=15 July 2009 |accessdate=4 January 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110429062052/http://www.ibtimes.com/contents/20090715/grown-emma-watson-models-burberry.htm |archivedate=2011年4月29日 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |author= |url=http://stylenews.peoplestylewatch.com/2010/01/05/emma-watsons-spring-summer-2010-burberry-ads-revealed/ |title=Emma Watson’s Spring/ Summer 2010 Burberry Ads Revealed! |publisher=Stylenews.peoplestylewatch.com |date=5 January 2010 |accessdate=4 January 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016172703/http://stylenews.peoplestylewatch.com/2010/01/05/emma-watsons-spring-summer-2010-burberry-ads-revealed/ |archive-date=2013-10-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>2010年开始，Burberry开始经营化妆品。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.graziadaily.co.uk/beauty/makeup/the-top-10-burberry-beauty-products-team-grazia-will-be-buying-from-burberrys-first-dedicated-beauty |title=The 10 Burberry Beauty Products We'll Be Buying From The Brand's First Dedicated Beauty Space |accessdate=2013-12-03 |archive-date=2013-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130512045227/http://www.graziadaily.co.uk/beauty/makeup/the-top-10-burberry-beauty-products-team-grazia-will-be-buying-from-burberrys-first-dedicated-beauty |dead-url=no }}</ref>

至2013年，Burberry营业额已增至20亿英镑，股票价值自上市起翻了三番，约值70亿英镑。<ref>{{cite news|title=Burberry Designer Bailey to Become CEO as Ahrendts Goes to Apple|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-10-15/burberry-says-bailey-to-become-ceo-as-ahrendts-leaves-for-apple.html|accessdate=15 October 2013|newspaper=Bloomberg|date=15 October 2013|author=Andrew Roberts|archive-date=2013-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131128144911/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-10-15/burberry-says-bailey-to-become-ceo-as-ahrendts-leaves-for-apple.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>虽然Burberry仍然鼓吹其英国联系，到2012年只有两家工厂仍在英国：一家在卡索佛德（Castleford）生产雨衣，另一家是在基利（Keighley）的小型工厂。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2012/jul/16/burberry-china-british-carole-cadwalladr |title=The Hypocrisy of Burberry's 'Made in Britain' appeal |accessdate=2013-12-03 |archive-date=2013-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019223625/http://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2012/jul/16/burberry-china-british-carole-cadwalladr |dead-url=no }}</ref>

Burberry於2013年開始提供Runway Made To Order服務，顧客於時裝秀結束後即可透過網路商店購買走秀款時裝與配件並提供個人訂製化服務，顧客可於購買商品上縫製個人吊牌或標記，同時亦是少數於時裝秀後即可購買最新時裝的精品品牌。

2018年3月，Riccardo Tisci接棒Christopher Bailey創作總監的位置，并更新Logo和印花标志。同年8月, Burberry在社群網站上公布新的品牌標誌<ref>[https://www.mings-fashion.com/burberry-riccardo-tisci-monogram-190933/ Riccardo Tisci推翻Burberry二十年不曾改過的標誌｜ 全新標誌是爲了融入高街風] {{Wayback|url=https://www.mings-fashion.com/burberry-riccardo-tisci-monogram-190933/ |date=20180902084257 }}  MING'S</ref>。同月，Tisci公布新的品牌方針，表示由9月發表的2019春夏季開始，品牌將全面停止使用動物皮草，同時也不會消毀滯銷的商品<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mings-fashion.com/burberry-riccardo-tisci-fur-free-204597/ |title=RICCARDO TISCI 宣布BURBERRY 新德政︰停止皮草及銷毀存貨 |accessdate=2018-09-10 |archive-date=2018-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180910094712/https://www.mings-fashion.com/burberry-riccardo-tisci-fur-free-204597/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

